00:04:12,725 --> 00:04:16,567
inherently fun. But most humans don't know they like learning,

88
00:04:16,607 --> 00:04:19,009
and that's why we must trick them. We have

89
00:04:19,029 --> 00:04:21,010
to make the player think they're playing the game

