00:05:45,316 --> 00:05:47,098
Instead of having the player read what they're going to do,

122
00:05:47,538 --> 00:05:48,879
why not have them do what they're going to do?

123
00:05:49,722 --> 00:05:53,843
The best way for the player to learn is by actually performing the actions within the game

