00:07:25,896 --> 00:07:27,076
Here's something we didn't want to do,

161
00:07:27,136 --> 00:07:29,677
which is just to put a message up on the screen that says,

162
00:07:30,618 --> 00:07:33,019
did you know you could use the shovel to dig up plants

163
00:07:33,039 --> 00:07:33,919
to replace it with others?

164
00:07:35,221 --> 00:07:38,905
Because for something so early and integral in the game,

165
00:07:39,666 --> 00:07:41,448
we really wanted to make sure players knew of it,

166
00:07:41,848 --> 00:07:44,711
because a message like this is pretty easy to miss.

167
00:07:45,412 --> 00:07:47,054
And we wanted to make sure they knew how to use it.

168
00:07:47,855 --> 00:07:49,456
So I began looking for a solution

169
00:07:49,657 --> 00:07:52,019
where the player would actually pick up the shovel and use it.

170
00:07:54,422 --> 00:07:55,603
So this was our first attempt.

171
00:07:56,821 --> 00:07:59,282
We knew we were giving out the shovel around level 1-5.

172
00:07:59,883 --> 00:08:02,244
And we also, coincidentally, knew we were going to have,

173
00:08:02,464 --> 00:08:05,006
we were going to want to have a minigame show up on level 1-5.

174
00:08:05,146 --> 00:08:08,268
So why not have the minigame teach the shovel mechanic,

175
00:08:08,328 --> 00:08:08,488
right?

176
00:08:09,408 --> 00:08:11,450
It's a great way to get the player to learn by doing.

177
00:08:12,910 --> 00:08:13,631
This minigame here.

178
00:08:14,431 --> 00:08:15,832
it placed a bunch of weeds on your lawn,

179
00:08:16,232 --> 00:08:19,394
and then it had you use your shovel to get rid of the weeds.

180
00:08:20,094 --> 00:08:22,496
This turned out to be not quite what we were looking for

181
00:08:22,556 --> 00:08:24,116
because it didn't really teach that,

182
00:08:24,917 --> 00:08:25,977
it didn't really teach that the shovel

183
00:08:26,017 --> 00:08:27,758
was for getting your plants out of the way

184
00:08:28,019 --> 00:08:28,999
so they could get replaced.

185
00:08:29,840 --> 00:08:31,300
Instead, it kind of taught the player,

186
00:08:32,261 --> 00:08:33,802
use the shovel to get rid of harmful things.

187
00:08:34,462 --> 00:08:37,304
And that's not the message we actually wanted to get across.

188
00:08:38,387 --> 00:08:44,150
So, attempt number two was to have Crazy Dave come and put walnuts all over your lawn.

189
00:08:44,531 --> 00:08:46,231
