00:08:47,172 --> 00:08:52,175
But the minigame itself had you using the shovel to make room for the pea shooters that

191
00:08:52,195 --> 00:08:53,375
would come down this conveyor belt here.

192
00:08:55,052 --> 00:08:59,616
While it did a good job of teaching players to use the shovel to remove stuff to make room for other plants,

